\mathbf{r}(t)=\left(2+\cos\frac{3}{2}t\right)\left(\begin{matrix}\cos t\\\sin t\end{matrix}\right)
\mathbf{r}(t_1)=\mathbf{r}(t_2),
\left(2+\cos\frac{3}{2}t_1\right)\cos t_1=\left(2+\cos\frac{3}{2}t_2\right)\cos t_2
\left(2+\cos\frac{3}{2}t_1\right)\sin t_1=\left(2+\cos\frac{3}{2}t_2\right)\sin t_2,
t\in [0,4\pi]
2 + \cos x
t_1+2\pi = t_2
2+\cos \frac 32t_1 = 2+\cos\frac 32 t_2
\cos\frac 32 t_1 = 0
\cos \frac 32t_2 = \cos(\frac 32 t_1 + 3\pi) = \cos(\frac 32 t_1 + \pi) = -\cos(\frac 32 t_1)
